# Untracked local files copied into each `claude --worktree` checkout.
# .gitignore syntax; ONLY files that are also gitignored get copied, so nothing
# tracked is duplicated. Without this a fresh worktree has no env/secrets and
# can't talk to Supabase / S3 / Stripe.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
apps/web/.env.local
.vercel
# Playwright auth state — skips the re-login `setup` project in a fresh worktree.
**/e2e/.auth
